  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Super Mini Mart</strong> is a <strong>wholesome</strong> and <strong>laid-back</strong> take on the management genre, leaving out the stress and only keeping good vibes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the new owner of the cutest bodega in town, you’ll get to supervise and manage all its daily activities and  transform this budding business into the thriving store all locals talk about!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1914060/extras/476e8a121d4310f1be203212987284d7.poster.avif?t=1761916340\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1914060/extras/476e8a121d4310f1be203212987284d7.webm?t=1761916340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1914060/extras/d0a9a966cbf09efbcd05c92aa6cc1967.webp?t=1761916340\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1914060/extras/d0a9a966cbf09efbcd05c92aa6cc1967.poster.avif?t=1761916340\" class=\"bb_img\" width=14 height=14 /></picture></span> <strong>Resupply</strong> and fill the aisles before the crowd gets in<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1914060/extras/77a5328afca6b6f6ec93e372cebbdcf4.webp?t=1761916340\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1914060/extras/77a5328afca6b6f6ec93e372cebbdcf4.poster.avif?t=1761916340\" class=\"bb_img\" width=14 height=14 /></picture></span> Use the <strong>varied appliances</strong> to keep your storeroom neat and your goods fresh<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1914060/extras/dd7855677d1b555198905966bcb82740.webp?t=1761916340\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1914060/extras/dd7855677d1b555198905966bcb82740.poster.avif?t=1761916340\" class=\"bb_img\" width=14 height=14 /></picture></span> <strong>Plan</strong> your stock and run discounts - all sale, no stale!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1914060/extras/a05f81d0e678594390976181902f5b68.webp?t=1761916340\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1914060/extras/a05f81d0e678594390976181902f5b68.poster.avif?t=1761916340\" class=\"bb_img\" width=14 height=14 /></picture></span> <strong>Grow</strong> your business and expand, from micro mart to mini mart - but never wall mart!<br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1914060/extras/d0a9a966cbf09efbcd05c92aa6cc1967.webp?t=1761916340\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1914060/extras/d0a9a966cbf09efbcd05c92aa6cc1967.poster.avif?t=1761916340\" class=\"bb_img\" width=14 height=14 /></picture></span> A <strong>colorful cast</strong> of endearing characters, each with their hopes, woes, and fav indulgences!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1914060/extras/77a5328afca6b6f6ec93e372cebbdcf4.webp?t=1761916340\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1914060/extras/77a5328afca6b6f6ec93e372cebbdcf4.poster.avif?t=1761916340\" class=\"bb_img\" width=14 height=14 /></picture></span> From outsider to <strong>community</strong>: gain the trust of your local customers and be rewarded with loyal friendships and unique storylines.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1914060/extras/dd7855677d1b555198905966bcb82740.webp?t=1761916340\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1914060/extras/dd7855677d1b555198905966bcb82740.poster.avif?t=1761916340\" class=\"bb_img\" width=14 height=14 /></picture></span> A lovely <strong>self-contained world</strong> in pastel colors, fat pixels and chirpy music <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1914060/extras/a05f81d0e678594390976181902f5b68.webp?t=1761916340\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1914060/extras/a05f81d0e678594390976181902f5b68.poster.avif?t=1761916340\" class=\"bb_img\" width=14 height=14 /></picture></span> The meaning of <strong>life</strong> - or at least, the minimart life.<br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1914060/extras/296409c50645d6cc2cfd3377487a1eb3.poster.avif?t=1761916340\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1914060/extras/296409c50645d6cc2cfd3377487a1eb3.webm?t=1761916340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1914060/extras/d0a9a966cbf09efbcd05c92aa6cc1967.webp?t=1761916340\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1914060/extras/d0a9a966cbf09efbcd05c92aa6cc1967.poster.avif?t=1761916340\" class=\"bb_img\" width=14 height=14 /></picture></span> Get those walls and floor to <strong>reflect your mood</strong>, one day blue and the other rainbow<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1914060/extras/77a5328afca6b6f6ec93e372cebbdcf4.webp?t=1761916340\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1914060/extras/77a5328afca6b6f6ec93e372cebbdcf4.poster.avif?t=1761916340\" class=\"bb_img\" width=14 height=14 /></picture></span> Buy new <strong>decorative</strong> elements to keep things as fresh as a ripe tomato<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1914060/extras/dd7855677d1b555198905966bcb82740.webp?t=1761916340\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1914060/extras/dd7855677d1b555198905966bcb82740.poster.avif?t=1761916340\" class=\"bb_img\" width=14 height=14 /></picture></span> Follow the theme of the <strong>seasons</strong>, from Spring lushness to Halloween spooks <br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s now time to roll up your sleeves and get those doors open o/<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And if you’d like to share your super mini creations, see what others made or simply chat with the devs, <strong>join our Discord now</strong>! <br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1914060/extras/40a1bb2b202c9e62b23b42d04e1b5e94.poster.avif?t=1761916340\" width=600 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1914060/extras/40a1bb2b202c9e62b23b42d04e1b5e94.webm?t=1761916340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1914060/extras/d1ee17130966c7610f5e24dfa3e82b23.poster.avif?t=1761916340\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1914060/extras/d1ee17130966c7610f5e24dfa3e82b23.webm?t=1761916340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></p></p>",
